        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Facilitating Investments in Local Markets Act of 2017 or the FILM Act of 2017</strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to extend through 2018 provisions that allow the expensing of the costs of qualified film, television, and live theatrical productions.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
